<subSubSection id="233364A0CC851417D7CBEBC36036B84E" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" type="notes">
<paragraph id="E0C53C849752D7A4FC1ACDAA395AA818" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2B616382A6DFCDCD08B37A720D9AC133" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
The subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="D1F84F475BC9750F6751808227D714B0" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Politophanes)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Politophanes">Bembidion Politophanes</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="77EF9AA6A1124D4C69863207A20C71B7" originalValue="Müller-Morzfeld">Mueller-Morzfeld</normalizedToken>
, 1998 was restored by 
<bibRefCitation id="D9EEDE41B308166CD20E8C69CD812025" author="Schmidt, J" journalOrPublisher="Entomologische Blaetter und Coleoptera," pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="361 - 406" refId="B50" refString="Schmidt, J, 2018. Alpha taxonomy from the Himalaya-Tibet orogen: New species and new synonymies in Bembidion Latreille, and a new key to species of the subgenus Bembidionetolitzkya Strand (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Bembidiini). Entomologische Blaetter und Coleoptera, 114: 361 - 406" title="Alpha taxonomy from the Himalaya-Tibet orogen: New species and new synonymies in Bembidion Latreille, and a new key to species of the subgenus Bembidionetolitzkya Strand (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Bembidiini)." volume="114" year="2018">Schmidt (2018)</bibRefCitation>
, after 
<bibRefCitation id="04918877CF8B6F0A53CCF612F0D342E3" author="Toledano, L" editor="Toledano, L" journalOrPublisher="Sezione Scienze della Vita" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="5 - 46" publicationUrl="http://www.museostorianaturaleverona.it/media/_Musei/_StoriaNaturale/_Allegati/Biblioteca/Altre%20pubblicazioni/Pubblicazioni%20collaboratori/Toledano/2008_Systematic_notes_Palaearctic_Bembidion_Latrelle.pdf" refId="B54" refString="Toledano, L, 2008. Systematic notes on the Palaearctic Bembidion Latreille, 1802 (Coleoptera, Carabidae) with particular reference to the fauna of China. In: Toledano, L, Ed., Contributions to the knowledge of the eastern Palaearctic Bembidiina (Insecta, Coleoptera, Carabidae). Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona 2. Serie. Sezione Scienze della Vita 18: 5 - 46, http://www.museostorianaturaleverona.it/media/_Musei/_StoriaNaturale/_Allegati/Biblioteca/Altre%20pubblicazioni/Pubblicazioni%20collaboratori/Toledano/2008_Systematic_notes_Palaearctic_Bembidion_Latrelle.pdf" title="Systematic notes on the Palaearctic Bembidion Latreille, 1802 (Coleoptera, Carabidae) with particular reference to the fauna of China." url="http://www.museostorianaturaleverona.it/media/_Musei/_StoriaNaturale/_Allegati/Biblioteca/Altre%20pubblicazioni/Pubblicazioni%20collaboratori/Toledano/2008_Systematic_notes_Palaearctic_Bembidion_Latrelle.pdf" volume="18" volumeTitle="Contributions to the knowledge of the eastern Palaearctic Bembidiina (Insecta, Coleoptera, Carabidae). Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona 2. Serie." year="2008">Toledano (2008)</bibRefCitation>
downgraded 
<taxonomicName id="D1AF3682742DC0153B7C57D90732B300" authorityName="Muller-Motzfeld" authorityYear="1998" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Politophanes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Politophanes" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66D42E745B3851DA8C76D63CFEBDAEB3" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Politophanes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to species group of subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="C6F2143633475457D7974CCFC8E71BB1" authority="Clairville, 1806" authorityName="Clairville" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Ocydromus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ocydromus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Ocydromus</taxonomicName>
Clairville, 1806. The subgenus includes the species that show particular endophallic characters (main sclerite from slightly arcuate to clearly bent, S-shaped, even long and coiled in a ring in the central portion in some species). 
<taxonomicName id="691661E3E7338B643555A0AC4B210CC2" authorityName="Bates" authorityYear="1873" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1873" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion chloreum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloreum">
<emphasis id="E41E772030E4F6CBD1D7BC0BB24D073C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion chloreum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, currently listed as member of subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="49379745B181EAF24AC43685324CD3A5" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Peryphus)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Peryphus">Bembidion Peryphus</taxonomicName>
, shows endophallic characters that clearly include it in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="62222BE817FA5D1242DA26B192A90023" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Politophanes)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Politophanes">Bembidion Politophanes</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="580494CAC16E0E0DFFA8FE4B0B9A1E30" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<taxonomicName id="5D065641806C176DD32C490D9201891B" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion sapporense" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sapporense">
<emphasis id="D4CFE5492265A61FD0536EAC32840FC6" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion sapporense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="6B7121448CC6E143AE8D2BA89B1861F3" originalValue="Jedlička">Jedlicka</normalizedToken>
, 1951, currently assigned to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="7A725443790318C9D138F627D51F0B18" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Asioperyphus)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Asioperyphus">Bembidion Asioperyphus</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="258D38819AF22BBD50E4BDA27BD43B94" originalValue="Vysoký">Vysoky</normalizedToken>
, 1986, was described from a single male specimen: we examined the holotype (NMPC) and, based on the aedeagal characters (long main sclerite, coiled in a ring at middle) we assign it to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="4CE2C6332F9F921083F6A7B0621CD4B4" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Politophanes)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Politophanes">Bembidion Politophanes</taxonomicName>
. The labels of the specimen (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="031A10FD8581A2B3DFD48728FC317B9B" captionStart="Figures 1–4" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figures 1 - 4. Habitus of 1 Bembidion (Peryphanes) sanatum Bates, 1883, holotype (NHMUK), 5.60 mm 2 B. (Plataphus) pseudolucillum Netolitzky, 1938 from Kibune, Kyoto (NHMW), 4.20 mm 3 B. (Peryphus) psuchrum Andrewes, 1935 Inde, Himachal Pradesh, Mahari, 3500 m (CTVR), 3.50 mm 4 labels of the holotype of Bembidion sapporense Jedlicka (NMPC). Photographs: Luca Toledano." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1044.62593.figures1-4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/555046" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">4</figureCitation>
) show that our colleague Seiji Morita (Tokyo), a specialist in Japanese 
<taxonomicName id="9347C9032A5F832515CAA92693A31963" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="? arthropoda" rank="family">Carabidae</taxonomicName>
, particularly in the 
<taxonomicName id="20B10E8109622CAF1614561CB0982A1B" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subTribe" subTribe="Bembidiina">Bembidiina</taxonomicName>
, identified the specimen as 
<taxonomicName id="6D916C03AED0DD13C6AE11D98318B5A8" authorityName="Bates" authorityYear="1873" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1873" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion chloreum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloreum">
<emphasis id="21370297DC6EFAD12C6B362133D24BCA" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion chloreum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Bates in 1991. Later he confirmed this identification and authorized us to state it formally here (Morita, pers. comm.): we are very grateful for that. Therefore we state the following synonymy: 
<taxonomicName id="FCC63DB65FAEAF3BB0B1C21631BEA9AC" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Asioperyphus) sapporense" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sapporense" subGenus="Asioperyphus">Bembidion (Asioperyphus) sapporense</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="9FA2B976852E2E74C0F5EA5285A6E111" originalValue="Jedlička">Jedlicka</normalizedToken>
, 1951 = 
<taxonomicName id="6543BC0F140CCBBD62F95286957F2981" authorityName="Bates" authorityYear="1873" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1873" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Politophanes) chloreum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloreum" subGenus="Politophanes">Bembidion (Politophanes) chloreum</taxonomicName>
Bates, 1873 syn. nov.
</paragraph>
